title: [Empath Guild, Alchemic Nexus]
description: This octagonal stone chamber is lit by eight flickering torches, one positioned at each corner.  A tunnel in the eastern wall leads upward toward the main training area.  A faint aroma wafts from each of six doorways, an unusual combination of ale and herbs.
paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, south, southwest, west, northwest, down, out
